profile:
Breathing new life into old furniture through various paint techniques and mediums. Transforming what once belonged to someone else into something fabulous.

I am Nicole Tyler and I have been refurbishing furniture for over 20 years. I have a passion for beautiful surroundings and making old things new again. I have had a passion for art ever since I was a young girl and discovered the outlet for painting when my oldest daughter was just a baby. I needed to make her furniture more modern and me. I have redone hundreds of pieces over the years and hope you enjoy my particular style. I love to use very unique colours and techniques.

If there is something particular you are looking for please contact me for details on how to make your furniture "Alternatively Yours".
